v0.7.3 (2018-08-07)
--------------------------------
 * Initial release with bladeRF Micro support
 * bladeRF Micro: Update pin-outs and constraints for Rev1.1+ PCBs
 * bladeRF Micro: Latch TX data going to the RFIC's DAC

